howItWorks: |
  <h2>How this paver calculator works</h2>
  <p>The calculator divides the patio area by the area of one paver, then adds overage for cuts, breakage, and layout waste.</p>
  <h2>Base gravel and sand</h2>
  <p>The calculator estimates base gravel and leveling sand using patio area &times; depth. Local soil, drainage, climate, and project load can change final requirements.</p>
